# Forbidden Planning Patterns

- Business logic inside UI
- Direct Firebase usage in widgets
- Tight Firebase coupling
- Shared mutable state
- Generic abstractions without need
- Oversized providers
- Monolithic repositories
- Missing error states
- Ignoring offline behavior
- Ignoring rollback strategy

